Loading data, save and dump using pig.

data = LOAD '/user/praveenbigdata19/pigdemo/data-bag.txt' using PigStorage(',');
DUMP data;
STORE data INTO '/user/praveenbigdata19/pigdemo/bigdata_store' USING PigStorage('|');



